{"word":"G1823 - ἐξαστράπτω - exastráptō - ex-as-trap'-to - Glistening","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξαστράπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exastráptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-as-trap'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Glistening</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரகாசி"},{"paragraph":"1. to send forth lightning, to lighten"},{"paragraph":"2. to flash out like lightning, to shine, be radiant"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G797 - ἀστράπτω - astráptō - as-trap'-to/797\">G797</a>; to <i>lighten forth</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>be radiant</i> (of very white garments): - glistening.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}